OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,FDespite hints the party's leader would
OL,7,Fbuild a case for a new road to tackle
OL,8,Fcongestion on the M4 around Newport,
OL,9,Fthe manifesto falls short of a firm
OL,10,Fpromise of a relief road.
OL,12,FInstead, it says the party is "clear
OL,13,Fabout the pressing need to renew the
OL,14,Fprocess of developing solutions to
OL,15,Fimprove the resilience of transport
OL,16,Flinks across the Menai Strait and
OL,17,Faddress congestion on the M4 around
OL,18,FNewport".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
