OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,F"We will cut NHS waiting times,
OL,7,Ffreeing up time, space and resources
OL,8,Fto build a sustainable and integrated
OL,9,Fhealth and care service for Wales `
OL,10,Fone that does more to keep people
OL,11,Fwell, rather than just treating
OL,12,Fillness.
OL,14,F"We'll support families and give every
OL,15,Fchild the best possible start through
OL,16,Fa transformational new free childcare
OL,17,Foffer for all children aged 9 months
OL,18,Fto 4 years old.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
