OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,F"We will unlock our untapped economic
OL,7,Fpotential ` building on our strengths
OL,8,Fto create well-paid and secure jobs
OL,9,Fand spread prosperity to every part of
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,F"And with a new, bold and determined
OL,13,Fdrive on numeracy and literacy skills,
OL,14,Fwe will raise the bar on standards in
OL,15,Four schools, so every child in Wales
OL,16,Fis set on the path to success."
OL,18,FOther plans include:
