OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,FAp Iowerth says his party are "ready
OL,7,Fto lead" what he called a "turning
OL,8,Fpoint" in which voters will be able to
OL,9,F"choose a new pathway" for Wales.
OL,11,FThe most recent YouGov polling for ITV
OL,12,FWales shows the party leading, with
OL,13,FReform UK 6% behind them in second
OL,14,Fplace. Seat projections in the same
OL,15,Fpoll suggest that this would result in
OL,16,Fthem being six seats short of a
OL,17,Fmajority.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
