OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,FThe leader previously declared the
OL,7,Felection a two-horse between Plaid
OL,8,FCymru and Reform UK. However, neither
OL,9,Fparty has yet been projected a
OL,10,Fmajority.
OL,12,FWhen asked about potential coalition
OL,13,Fpartners Ap Iorwerth has stated
OL,14,Fambitions to form a "progressive
OL,15,Falliance" and ruled out any agreement
OL,16,Fwith "parties on the right".
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@IO]
