OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,FReacting to the manifesto, a Welsh
OL,7,FLabour spokesperson said: "Plaid Cymru
OL,8,Fshould be honest with voters. They
OL,9,Fclaim not to be focusing on
OL,10,Findependence in this election and yet
OL,11,Ftheir manifesto explicitly sets out a
OL,12,Froute map towards independence. They
OL,13,Fnow need to explain this deception to
OL,14,Fthe people of Wales in the coming
OL,15,Fweeks.
OL,26,@oD@[OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
