PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776096667
OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,F"They are also misleading the public
OL,7,Fon the voting system, pitting it as a
OL,8,Ftwo-horse race in a proportional
OL,9,Fvoting system. And they are misleading
OL,10,Fpeople on the deliverability of their
OL,11,Fpledges, particularly on childcare -
OL,12,Fwhich is simply not affordable under
OL,13,Ftheir plans."
OL,15,FDan Thomas, Reform Wales leader, says
OL,16,FPlaid share responsibility for the
OL,17,Fstate of Wales' public services after
OL,18,F"propping Labour up in Cardiff Bay for
OL,19,Fa generation".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
