SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776096667
OL,3,CWales can stand on its own two feet,
OL,4,CPlaid leader says
OL,6,FHe added: "They are the problem, not
OL,7,Fthe solution. Only Reform has a
OL,8,Fcredible and ambitious plan to give
OL,9,FWales the fresh start it deserves."
OL,11,FA Welsh Liberal Democrat spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid Plaid Cymru are being
OL,13,F"fundamentally dishonest with people
OL,14,Fabout the true cost of their plans for
OL,15,Findependence", adding, "we've already
OL,16,Fseen in Scotland how the SNP and
OL,17,FGreens spent years of political energy
OL,18,Fand taxpayers' money focused on
OL,19,Findependence instead of fixing
OL,20,Fstruggling public services."
